videos.description: Dallas Walton knocks down a 3-pointer that puts Colorado up six against #14 Arizona.
videos.headline: Walton's 3 fires up Colorado crowd

videos.description: Dallas Walton takes a dish from McKinley Wright IV and finishes the layup.
videos.headline: Colorado's Walton finishes pick-and-roll with layup

videos.description: Tad Boyle says that the Buffaloes need to keep rebounding well and taking good shots to maintain their lead over Arizona.
videos.headline: Boyle looking to keep aggressive offense in 2nd half

videos.description: Deandre Ayton steals a pass that leads to Rawle Alkins hitting a jumper off the glass.
videos.headline: Alkins banks it home for Arizona

videos.description: Deandre Ayton throws down a big dunk to set up 3-point play as Arizona cuts into Colorado's lead.
videos.headline: Ayton slams home dunk, draws foul

videos.description: On a fast break, Allonzo Trier hits an off-balance shot while falling to the ground.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier hits circus shot

videos.description: Dallas Walton takes the pass under the basket and makes a nice move to sink a fadeaway jumper to extend Colorado's lead.
videos.headline: Walton hits clutch shot in traffic
